{"title":"IncDec Sequence","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":62,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2498","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>　　<span>给定一个长度为n的数列{a1,a2...an}，每次可以选择一个区间[l,r]，使这个区间内的数都加一或者都减一。</span><br><span>　　问至少需要多少次操作才能使数列中的所有数都一样,并求出在保证最少次数的前提下,最终得到的数列有多少种。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>　　第一行一个正整数n </span><br><span>　　接下来n行,每行一个整数,第i+1行的整数表示ai。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>　　<span>第一行输出最少操作次数</span><br /><span>　　第二行输出最终能得到多少种结果</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4<br>1<br>1<br>2<br>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1<br>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>　　对于100%的数据，n=100000，0&lt;=ai&lt;2147483648。</span></p>\n<p><span><br></span></p>\n<p><span>来源：Nescafe 22</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}